1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:15,039 --> 00:00:15,919
I'm getting you out.

4
00:00:18,679 --> 00:00:19,800
Where are you taking...

5
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,120
Stay out of it.

6
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,559
It's dangerous!

7
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,560
Qiao Nian!

8
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:39,159
Why are you here?

9
00:00:39,159 --> 00:00:39,920
Where's Qiao Nian?

10
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,240
She left with Jiang Zechen.

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,840
So I'm later than him again, isn't it?

12
00:00:45,119 --> 00:00:45,920
(Three years ago)
Qiao Nian,

13
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:49,240
your status and influence
in the Qiao family

14
00:00:49,359 --> 00:00:50,560
is the same as Duan Yiran's.

15
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,600
Why do you let her walk all over you?

16
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:57,439
Because I don't want
to cause trouble for Grandpa.

17
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,679
I don't want to live
in constant fighting too.

18
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:01,960
Qiao Nian.

19
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,760
I heard Duan Yiran came after you again.

20
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,719
So I'm late again, huh?

21
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:26,400
Don't ever do something
this dangerous again.

22
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,760
Does it still hurt?

23
00:01:37,519 --> 00:01:38,959
What happened...

24
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:42,640
I don't know what happened.

25
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,799
It just appeared out of nowhere.

26
00:01:48,719 --> 00:01:49,519
Hey.

27
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:52,359
Our wounds are in the exact same place.

28
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:55,079
That's strange.

29
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:57,920
Every time I see fire or fireworks,

30
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,519
I recover fragments of memory.

31
00:02:00,079 --> 00:02:02,840
I remembered the day Grandpa passed
when we were in the hospital.

32
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:54,719
Qiao Nian.

33
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,719
Song Che.

34
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,759
Grandpa...

35
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:12,639
He's gone, isn't he?

36
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,400
I don't know why,

37
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,599
but I feel like I can see him

38
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,520
when I look at the fireworks.

39
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:29,840
- Nian.
- Grandpa.

40
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:32,240
You must be careful of Wenjun.

41
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:36,800
You've suffered all these years.

42
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:39,360
No. I'm fine.

43
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,400
Nian, get out!

44
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,159
Grandpa!

45
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,560
I remember what happened to him.

46
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,680
My heart hurts so much.

47
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,039
It's her.

48
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,639
It's Qiao Wenjun.

49
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:09,840
She killed Grandpa.

50
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:14,520
This time,
I saw my consciousness left my body

51
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,919
and attached itself to you.

52
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,240
Did that happen?

53
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,120
Yes.

54
00:04:20,319 --> 00:04:22,279
Before I rushed into the fire,

55
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:25,360
I already felt the searing heat
burning my skin.

56
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:30,279
It must be a shared perception.

57
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:33,240
Hard to believe, right?

58
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,319
It's hard to explain this right now.

59
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,759
I'll break it down for you later.

60
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:47,040
Oh, there's something urgent
I need to tell you.

61
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:51,560
Bai Niansheng gave me this.

62
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:55,920
It's the surveillance footage
of your grandpa's fire.

63
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:04,800
But Qiao Wenjun
controls the company now.

64
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:09,079
I can't do anything about her
with this evidence alone.

65
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,480
What do you want to do?

66
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,000
I need a stronger proof

67
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,480
to take her down in one move.

68
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:18,279
Would you consider
working with Jiang Group?

69
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,480
Hmm?

70
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,480
After all, the enemy
of my enemy is a friend.

71
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,759
What...

72
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:34,399
are you doing?

73
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:41,600
Do you remember when you
couldn't find your mom?

74
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,920
You were crouched there,
crying your eyes out.

75
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:50,839
I swore back then I would protect you.

76
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,360
Nian,

77
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:56,439
please believe me.

78
00:05:57,959 --> 00:06:00,199
(He must be only saying this)

79
00:06:00,199 --> 00:06:01,480
(to make me work with him.)

80
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:07,240
Qiao Nian.

81
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,160
Hmm?

82
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:19,500
(Jiang Xiao: When are you
bringing Nian back home?)

83
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:25,240
(Jiang Zechen won't work
with Qiao Wenjun for no reason.)

84
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,360
(Jiang Group's interest
must be behind this.)

85
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:31,319
(Maybe Jiang Xiao is the one
pulling the strings here.)

86
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:36,480
You asked
if I'd consider working with you.

87
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,839
Have you decided?

88
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,439
I'll think about it.

89
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:51,319
Jiang Zechen,
you called for me so urgently.

90
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:52,160
What's the issue?

91
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,680
A man named Song Che has appeared
in Qiao Nian's life.

92
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,160
Watch him. Find out what he wants.

93
00:06:57,759 --> 00:06:59,720
Why don't you watch your wife yourself?

94
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,879
I don't know why,

95
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:03,170
but her memories of the recent past
have all disappeared.

96
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,680
She lost her memories?

97
00:07:05,839 --> 00:07:07,240
So to protect her safety,

98
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:09,480
I need to see my dad now

99
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,959
and use him
to keep Qiao Wenjun in check.

100
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:14,639
You're the perfect husband.

101
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:17,560
Don't worry.
I'll keep a close eye on Song Che.

102
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:22,839
(Jiang Zechen, just watch.)

103
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,439
(I'm going to mess with him so much.)

104
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,319
Who are you? Move.

105
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,959
Who exactly are you?

106
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,040
Why are you blocking me?

107
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:44,199
Why do you keep
following Qiao Nian around?

108
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,199
You know her?

109
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,839
Who sent you?

110
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,160
Jiang Zechen.

111
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,160
Move aside.

112
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,079
No!

113
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:58,560
You jerk!

114
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:02,959
You left me alone overseas for so long

115
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:05,160
and even ran off at our wedding.

116
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:07,279
Was it all just to see this woman?

117
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,360
Song Che,

118
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:11,519
I came here to get an answer.

119
00:08:11,959 --> 00:08:14,360
Are you going to marry me or not?

120
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,439
Sorry to interrupt.

121
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,319
Get back here!

122
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,360
You crazy woman.

123
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,279
Stop talking nonsense or else!

124
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:24,720
Argh!

125
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,920
You crazy woman.

126
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,639
Hello.

127
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:41,159
Hi, Mr. Song. Are you free to meet?

128
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,720
Ms. Qiao, I'm happy

129
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,840
to see you're safe.

130
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:51,200
Mr. Qiao wanted to see you so much
before he passed.

131
00:08:51,799 --> 00:08:53,320
What a pity.

132
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,159
Have a seat.

133
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,399
Okay.

134
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,600
Mr. Zhou.

135
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,120
Yes.

136
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:04,080
I know what happened to Grandpa.

137
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,879
So what exactly is going on
with the company?

138
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,120
Ever since Qiao Wenjun took power,

139
00:09:09,399 --> 00:09:12,320
she replaced all yours
and Mr. Qiao's people.

140
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,919
She has total control
of the company now.

141
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,480
Qiao Wenjun...

142
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,879
Do you know
what she's been up to lately?

143
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:27,480
She's been working on Dolphi Beauty.

144
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:30,159
That's the brand I created for Mom.

145
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,720
How dare she touch it?

146
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,720
Ms. Qiao, don't act rashly.

147
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,759
After Qiao Wenjun
seized Mr. Qiao's shares,

148
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:41,399
she's the company's
largest shareholder now.

149
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,399
Oh.

150
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,159
If she discovers you're back,

151
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,679
she might even try to harm you.

152
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,519
That's exactly what I want.

153
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,759
Mr. Zhou.

154
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:54,440
Yes.

155
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,440
I need your help with something.

156
00:09:57,039 --> 00:10:00,080
I knew I couldn't stop you.

157
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,900
I suppose this is for the best.

158
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:05,559
We can't let Qiao Wenjun
control the company forever.

159
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,600
Ms. Qiao, tell me.

160
00:10:06,610 --> 00:10:07,680
What do you need me to do?

161
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,799
(I will get rid of that vicious mother)

162
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,679
(and daughter one by one.)

163
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:24,090
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

164
00:10:24,370 --> 00:10:31,970
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

165
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:35,810
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

166
00:10:36,330 --> 00:10:39,610
♪Where this ends♪

167
00:10:39,610 --> 00:10:46,890
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

168
00:10:46,890 --> 00:10:51,220
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

169
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:54,340
♪Love turns into pain♪

170
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:58,530
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

171
00:10:58,690 --> 00:11:02,170
♪Yet I still want you close♪

172
00:11:02,170 --> 00:11:06,340
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

173
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:09,650
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

174
00:11:09,650 --> 00:11:14,220
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

175
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:20,530
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

176
